cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.SOC, cs.HC 

The paper focuses on analyzing communication data within an online creative community for collaborative songwriting. This falls under the category of computational creativity (cs.CY) as well as social and information networks (cs.SI) since the study involves analyzing the communication network within the community. Additionally, the study involves data mining (cs.SD) and social computing (cs.SOC) since it investigates how comment-based communication shapes members' behavior. Finally, the study also involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) since it deals with online communities and user behavior.
